item.title: Prayer bpn10411 in Kiribati
item.description: Ko noorai, au Uea, ma moau are e rairaki nakon karawan Am tituaraoi ao marawan Am bwain aakoi, ni bubai man bwaai ni kabane i Rarikim. I Butiiko, ni mimitongin Taain Am Kaotioti i aon Tiinai, ao ni korakoran ootan Tobibin Am raoiroi are e ootanako man rabin karawan Aram, are te Kakabwarai buure ao ni bwaina te atataiaomata nakoiu. Korobokiia i bukiu, ngkanne, n Am kainikoroboki ni mimitong baike a na karietataai rinanon Aram n aonaaban te karikibwai.
